data.description: Seller motivated, living out of state. This 3-bedroom 2 bath Ranch house is fenced with a large, shaded wrap around driveway, 2 car attached garage. In back is a 3-car garage with carport, also beside it is a large 10 x 16 tool shed. Plenty of parking with this very large concrete driveway. Nice yard between the house and back buildings and large yard behind back buildings. House and buildings all have new roofs. Property is situated in county limits. You're not just getting a house; you're getting a compound. This is a very unique property, must come and see!
